cards.title: Sacred Games
cards.content: Sacred Games is a critically acclaimed Indian web television series that premiered on Netflix in 2018. It is based on a 2006 novel of the same name by Vikram Chandra.

cards.title: 13 Reasons Why
cards.content: 13 Reasons Why is a Netflix original series that premiered in 2017. It is based on the 2007 young adult novel of the same name by Jay Asher. The series is produced by Selena Gomez and stars Dylan Minnette, Katherine Langford, and Christian Navarro.

cards.title: The Boys
cards.content: The Boys is an American superhero web television series that premiered on Amazon Prime Video in 2019. It is based on a comic book series of the same name by Garth Ennis and Darick Robertson.

cards.title: Antman
cards.content: Ant-Man is a superhero film based on the Marvel Comics character of the same name. It was released in 2015 and is part of the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU).

cards.title: Intersteller
cards.content: Interstellar is a 2014 science fiction film directed by Christopher Nolan and starring Matthew McConaughey, Anne Hathaway, and Jessica Chastain.
